title: Are You Still Sitting Around?
itunes:title: Are You Still Sitting Around?
description:
Episode 564 - Are you still sitting around studying and not getting things done? Education for anything is important but we all get to a point were we need to stop learning and start doing. In this episode, I will teach you how to learn when it is time to get off your butt and just get work done!
